python-rex changelog
====================

0.4
---
* Added attribute "group" to rex function object holding last regex's RexMatch object
* RexMatch bug fix (default value when using get())
* Added py3 support
* Added tox tests across py26, py27, py33
* Test refactoring to py.test

0.3.1
-----
* RexMatch refactoring and bug fix (empty match is represented as empty string)

0.3
---
* rex orthodox mode (using rex without == operator)

0.2
---
* rex caching (as test with csvkit, it can speed up processing heavily reusing same pattern by 10%)

0.1.1
-----
* fixing packaging problem

0.1
---
* initial version
* matching and substitution
* tests
